    "text": "Stop Harmful and Abusive Telecommunications Expression Act of 2019 or the Stop HATE Act of 2019\n\nThis bill requires the National Telecommunications and Information Administration to report on and make recommendations to address the role of telecommunications in violent acts and hate crimes against individuals or groups on the basis of race, gender and gender identity, religion, disability, sexual orientation, ethnicity, color, or national origin."
